parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden separation of the convertible roof can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The roof detaches from the vehicle while driving
roof panel separates from the frame
inability to drive with the top up
and potential damage to the vehicle or surrounding objects.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: LED-Based Turn Signal Failure in Rear Tail Lamp Assembly
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turn signal in the left rear tail lamp assembly can render the vehicle unsafe and illegal to drive, as it does not meet safety standards.
symptoms: The turn signal in the left rear tail lamp assembly does not function
the LED light is not illuminated
the turn signal is not visible to other drivers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the engine to stall without warning, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: the fuel gauge does not display accurate fuel readings
the fuel pressure at the fuel rail test port is aerated and low (around 15psi)
the engine will not run at this point.
